  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on a unique challenge in this physics-based pogo stick platformer! Join an ever expanding gang of POGOPPL as you bounce through the sunny streets of Pogo City. Although it was built to be a haven for pogo-enthusiasts, lately things in Pogo City have taken a dark turn. Laser barriers and obstacles of all kinds are being deployed to eradicate pogo activity in the city. So hop on your pogo stick, solo or with friends, and uncover this diabolical plot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JOIN THE POGOPPL, AND TAKE BACK POGO CITY!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/3b06b1672acbaa9e8fc9cfdecaa5672c.poster.avif?t=1746004291\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/3b06b1672acbaa9e8fc9cfdecaa5672c.webm?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/3b06b1672acbaa9e8fc9cfdecaa5672c.mp4?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A STORY MODE set across 70 levels of varied challenges, mini-games, boss fights, twists, turns, chaos and madness!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/cb7f1d17291b57063a5d3ea686a68b5a.poster.avif?t=1746004291\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/cb7f1d17291b57063a5d3ea686a68b5a.webm?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/cb7f1d17291b57063a5d3ea686a68b5a.mp4?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 6-PLAYER LOCAL MULTIPLAYER! Experience the story with your friends or challenge them to a fight in POGO KOMBAT! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/b67b516b52262b3f227876dce4b6b43e.poster.avif?t=1746004291\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/b67b516b52262b3f227876dce4b6b43e.webm?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/b67b516b52262b3f227876dce4b6b43e.mp4?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An easy-to-use LEVEL EDITOR! Download new levels from the Steam Workshop, or share your own creations! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/7e787973062a74e29eb44229528af093.poster.avif?t=1746004291\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/7e787973062a74e29eb44229528af093.webm?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/7e787973062a74e29eb44229528af093.mp4?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on a unique challenge in this physics-based pogo stick platformer! Join an ever expanding gang of POGOPPL as you bounce through the sunny streets of Pogo City. Although it was built to be a haven for pogo-enthusiasts, lately things in Pogo City have taken a dark turn. Laser barriers and obstacles of all kinds are being deployed to eradicate pogo activity in the city. So hop on your pogo stick, solo or with friends, and uncover this diabolical plot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JOIN THE POGOPPL, AND TAKE BACK POGO CITY!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/3b06b1672acbaa9e8fc9cfdecaa5672c.poster.avif?t=1746004291\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/3b06b1672acbaa9e8fc9cfdecaa5672c.webm?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/3b06b1672acbaa9e8fc9cfdecaa5672c.mp4?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A STORY MODE set across 70 levels of varied challenges, mini-games, boss fights, twists, turns, chaos and madness!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/cb7f1d17291b57063a5d3ea686a68b5a.poster.avif?t=1746004291\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/cb7f1d17291b57063a5d3ea686a68b5a.webm?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/cb7f1d17291b57063a5d3ea686a68b5a.mp4?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 6-PLAYER LOCAL MULTIPLAYER! Experience the story with your friends or challenge them to a fight in POGO KOMBAT! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/b67b516b52262b3f227876dce4b6b43e.poster.avif?t=1746004291\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/b67b516b52262b3f227876dce4b6b43e.webm?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/b67b516b52262b3f227876dce4b6b43e.mp4?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An easy-to-use LEVEL EDITOR! Download new levels from the Steam Workshop, or share your own creations! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/7e787973062a74e29eb44229528af093.poster.avif?t=1746004291\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/7e787973062a74e29eb44229528af093.webm?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640220/extras/7e787973062a74e29eb44229528af093.mp4?t=1746004291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
